headline: Zimmer Biomet to Present at the 43rd Annual J.P. Morgan Healthcare Conference
summary: Zimmer Biomet Holdings, Inc. (NYSE and SIX: ZBH) today announced that members of the Zimmer Biomet management team will be presenting at the 43rd Annual J.P. Morgan Healthcare Conference on Tuesday, January 14, 2025, at 8:15 a.m. PT (11:15 a.m. ET).
